Loch Eilt has been used as a location in several films. It was used as [Dumbledore](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dumbledore)'s grave, which was later, digitally placed on [Loch Arkaig](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Loch_Arkaig).
